Thank you for visiting. This tutorial describes a Ruby on Rails application with a mobile application UI written using the Sencha Touch Framework. Please look at the blog posts at http://mikehoitomt.wordpress.com/2011/03/10/sencha-touch-application-with-ruby-on-rails-part-1/ and http://mikehoitomt.wordpress.com/2011/04/21/sencha-touch-application-with-ruby-on-rails-%E2%80%93-part-2/